headline: Eos Energy Enterprises, Inc. (EOSE) Reports Q2 Loss, Lags Revenue Estimates
summary: Eos Energy Enterprises (EOSE) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -517.65% and -28.41%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: GRAINGER DECLARES QUARTERLY DIVIDEND
summary: W.W. Grainger, Inc. (NYSE: GWW) today announced its board of directors has approved a quarterly cash dividend of $2.26 per share. The dividend is payable on September 1, 2025, to shareholders of record on August 11, 2025.
